source.name: LIONS NATIONAL CASELOAD STATISTICAL DATA
source.description: The Executive Office for U.S. Attorneys regularly releases national caseload statistical data in response to monthly requests under the Freedom of Information and Privacy Acts. To facilitate public access, the data appears below pursuant to 5 U.S.C. §552(a)(2)(D).
